{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/getTmpDir()","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getTmpDir"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}],"roleHeading":"Function","externalID":"s:4GLib9getTmpDirSSSgyF","title":"getTmpDir()","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"func"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/gettmpdir()"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Gets the directory to use for temporary files.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"getTmpDir","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On UNIX, this is taken from the "},{"code":"TMPDIR","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" environment variable."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"If the variable is not set, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"P_tmpdir"},{"type":"text","text":" is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"used, as defined by the system C library. Failing that, a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"hard-coded default of “\/tmp” is returned."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On Windows, the "},{"code":"TEMP","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" environment variable is used, with the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"root directory of the Windows installation (eg: “C:\") used"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as a default.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The encoding of the returned string is system-defined. On Windows,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it is always UTF-8. The return value is never "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" or the empty"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"string."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"url":"\/documentation\/glib","kind":"symbol","title":"GLib","abstract":[],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","role":"collection"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/getTmpDir()":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/getTmpDir()","title":"getTmpDir()","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Gets the directory to use for temporary files."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"getTmpDir","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}],"url":"\/documentation\/glib\/gettmpdir()"}}}